Charles West (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_West_(actor) 0 Charles West (November 30, 1885 – October 10, 1943) was an American film actor of the silent film era. He appeared in more than 300 films between 1908 and 1937. He was born in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania and died in Los Angeles, California.
